  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.5.9">
<l>toṇṭāyār tāmparavu maṭiyi ṉāṉaip paṭikaṭanta tāḷāḷaṟ kāḷā yuytal</l>
<l>viṇṭāṉait teṉṉilaṅkai yarakkar vēntai vilaṅkuṇṇa valaṅkaivāyc caraṅka ḷāṇṭu</l>
<l>paṇṭāya vētaṅkaḷ nāṉku maintu vēḷvikaḷuṅ kēḷviyō ṭaṅka māṟum</l>
<l>kaṇṭāṉait toṇṭaṉēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ kaṭipoḻilcūḻ kaṭalmallait talaca yaṉattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Him who declared the four ancient Vedas, the five sacrifices,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the six branches of knowledge,</l>
<l>Having discharged arrows from his right hand at the king of demons</l>
<l rend="indent">of southern Lanka, [like] when he snatched animals [of prey],</l>
<l>At the one who rejected the salvation of becoming a devotee to him</l>
<l rend="indent">whose feet measured the world, him whose feet [his] servants praise,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself in Talacayaṉam encircled by fragrant gardens</l>
<l rend="indent">at Mallai by the sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
